Fashion Search AI
Description
Fashion Search AI is a Python-based tool designed to help users find and recommend fashion items, specifically kurta sets, based on their descriptions. It uses a combination of natural language processing (NLP) and AI models to search a dataset of fashion items and generate recommendations. The tool also visualizes product images to enhance the user experience.

